" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗱 你自己唔肯去面對 唔肯去改啫"},{"pid":"87b0dd5628c7a5b433de4b3ecb59d9de80933750","tid":190752,"uid":101997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"我明你嘅感受<br />\n我都返過啲西工<br />\n啲人好撚西<br />\n我本身唔毒＆多嘢講<br />\n但其實如果啲老師忽會恰你都係會恰<br />\n所以你都唔洗咁介意，事實未必真係因為你問題<br />\n祝你之後揾到份好啲嘅工、有啲好啲嘅同事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed8bb107d67422e06f12eb4c9b298d5ffb943ba","tid":190752,"uid":101997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"我打錯字㖭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔係老師忽，係老屎忽"},{"pid":"e06267f3e5c1611d2712ec4bed641878b5220f23","tid":190752,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"點解呢個世界咁多仆街?"}]}